    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8 and a 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS step-less adjustment, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis is equipped with the factory M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring optimal lateral grip and suspension geometry under load. Maintained with technical care, the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed, preserving the mechanical integrity of this iconic performance platform.",
