    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW X5 is a prime example of a well-maintained luxury SUV, striking the perfect balance between utility and elegance. The Alpine White exterior maintains a brilliant luster, complemented by 19-inch alloy wheels wrapped in tires with significant tread remaining. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather interior is exceptionally clean, with the seat bolsters showing only minimal evidence of use and the cabin remaining entirely smoke-free. All electronic components, including the iDrive navigation and the panoramic glass roof, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and the transmission shifts with factory smoothness. I have kept a comprehensive folder of service records, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection performed by a certified technician. This car has been garage-kept and treated with respect, making it a reliable and sophisticated choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
