      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road today? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and has been super dependable for all my errands and weekend trips. It\u2019s got that perfectly broken-in feel\u2014solid, comfortable, and really well-cared for. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come say hi and take it for a test drive!",
